dc_title_s: Pigot & Co.s new map of the environs of London extending 14 miles round St. Pauls in every direction; published by J. Pigot & Co.
dc_description_s: Includes view of the Thames River below map. 1 map; 40 cm diam., on sheet 50 x 44 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
